              necessity. But oftentimes it can be a lot of extra work you
              probably don't need, even just to host a minimal setup.
            </p>
            <p class="m-0">
              With Metabase Cloud, we'll take care of everything, and if you're
              on
              <a class="d-inline blue-link-hover text-bold" href="/pricing/"
                >Pro or Enterprise</a
